==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inglobate
<hw>In*glo"bate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>In the form of a
globe or sphere; -- applied to nebulous matter collected into a sphere
by the force of gravitation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inglobe</ent>⟦br⟧
